Description: A lightweight Python IDE for modern development
 Pythonico is a modern Python IDE built with PyQt6 that provides:
 .
  * Advanced syntax highlighting with Tokyo Night themes
  * Intelligent auto-completion with contextual suggestions
  * Integrated Claude AI assistant for code help
  * Built-in Python terminal and REPL
  * Project explorer with file management
  * Advanced debugging capabilities
  * Split view editing
  * Find and replace functionality
  * Customizable themes and fonts
  * Session management
 .
 This IDE is designed for developers who want a lightweight yet feature-rich
 Python development environment with modern UI and AI assistance.
 .
 Note: For full functionality, some optional dependencies need to be installed
 manually via pip: anthropic, speechrecognition, pyqtconsole
